Another one 
Trouble with Sons: A woman had two sons who were born on the same
hour of the same day of the same year. But they were not twins. How
could this be so?
solution no.:1
the two boys are half-brothers i.e. born to two different wives of the same man

solution no.:2
you have specified the same day of the year and not the same day of the same month of the same year.this may be interprated as being two different mondays of say,january and december properly separated by the gestation period of 270 days for human beings.
