-----------------------------------
oh kay got it!

3 to the power 2 = 5 + 4

hope this one's right! :mg:

If more functions are to be used along with 2,3,4,5 and +, = then there are
n to the power n solutions.

(2+3) = ceiling(4.5) 
etc. etc.

