It was Einstein who originally showed that being accelerated is equivalent to
being in a gravitational field (apologies to any mathematicians and physicists
present - this is simplified but basically correct!).

Ans for the puzzle 
There is a car with a very flat roof, on a level road.  ..Assume windows are 
closed, and ...the wind from outside.

So just as on the Earth a helium balloon will rise UP (i.e. opposed to the force
of gravity) because the surrounding air is heavier, so too will it move to the
front of the car, for the same reason.

