RahulSharma
Sun Jul 18, 2004 6:46 pm


-----------------------------------
ADVERTISEMENT
 
 
Which is bigger 999! or 500^999

999!=999*1*998*2*...=(500^2-499^2)*(500^2-498^2)*...500 such terms

Obviously, 500^999 is bigger!

