"every day for a month i shall bring you rs. 5,00,000.of course i will want something in return ,u pay me 1 paise on day ,2 paise second ,4 on third and so on . if the deal is aceptable to u ,shall we commence tommorow ?
johri lal ,equally shrewed ,said that he had to go out for some days ,can we go ahead eith this business next month ??heera lal declined ...why????

