These 2 puzzles were asked to me in Inductis Interview :mg:

Solve them :-

1. There are 25 horses and in what min no of races can u find top three of them
The constraints are that in one race u can race 5 of the horses and u dont have a timer...

2. A camel has 3000 banans, he has to take those from A to B and B is 1000 miles away from A
The camel can take 1000 bananas with him at a time and for every mile it needs one banana to eat...
What max no of bananas can it take to B...

:mg:
-Akshat

